fields.search:
select count(*) AS num_visits, w.page_visited FROM
(
select regexp_extract(httpinfo, '([^ ]+) ([^ ]+)', 2) AS page_visited,
       regexp_extract(httpinfo, '([^ ]+) /([^/ ]+)', 2) AS top_dir
from apache2.weblogs
where httpinfo rlike '^GET'
AND httpinfo not like '%/wp-%'
) w
WHERE w.top_dir in ('artist', 'artists', 'products', 'issue', 'issues', 'author')
OR w.top_dir rlike '[0-9]{4}'
GROUP BY w.page_visited
ORDER BY count(*) DESC
